The paper deals with the transmission of instructions from a thread to a remote execution environment, which involves issues related to programming languages (cs.PL), distributed computing (cs.Distributed), operating systems (cs.OS), and network infrastructure (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of protocols for efficient transmission, which is a topic of interest in the area of distributed computing (cs.DC).
